'''Tank Ex'''或 '''MBT Ex'''是印度[[國防研究及發展組織|國防研究及發展組織]]于2002年提出的一种[[主战坦克|主战坦克]]方案。据传言其名字为''[[迦尔纳|迦尔纳]]''，史诗[[摩诃婆罗多|摩诃婆罗多]]中的一个英雄。<ref name="MJ1">{{cite web |url=http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/india/tank-ex.htm |title=MBT-EX / Tank-Ex / Karna |work=globalsecurity.org |accessdate=2014-05-03 |archive-date=2009-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090205092552/http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/india/tank-ex.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="MJ2">{{cite web |url=http://www.military-today.com/tanks/tank_ex.htm |title=Tank Ex |work=military-today.com |accessdate=2014-05-03 |archive-date=2012-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120510170135/http://www.military-today.com/tanks/tank_ex.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>它是继Ajeya坦克（T-72改型）后DRDO再一次打算尝试制作一版T-72改进型坦克。<ref name="MJ3">{{cite web |url=http://www.bharat-rakshak.com/LAND-FORCES/Equipment/Others/351-Tank-Ex.html |title=Tank-EX: DRDO's New Tank |work=bharat-rakshak.com |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120304085514/http://www.bharat-rakshak.com/LAND-FORCES/Equipment/Others/351-Tank-Ex.html |archivedate=2012-03-04 |accessdate=2014-05-03 }}</ref> 它制造了两个样车，进行了半年的测试并表现良好，但是印度陆军没采用它。<ref name="MJ2"/>

